summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of OktaSkill EdTech multi-page marketing website. All 16 required features tested successfully including navigation, forms, routing, mobile responsiveness, and legal pages.
passed_tests: Home page loads with hero section, services grid (12 cards), trusted brands (5 brands), top consultants (4 cards), and CTA section
Navigation bar with all required links: Find Work, Hire Talent, Discover Insights, Why Us, Refer & Earn, Contact Us
Service detail page navigation works (/service/finance tested)
Find Talent Form has all required fields: email, name, mobile, company, hear about us dropdown, requirements dropdown, description
Find Work Form has all required fields: email, name, mobile, hear about us dropdown, requirements dropdown, LinkedIn profile, resume upload, description
Legal page with working tab navigation (Terms & Conditions, Privacy Policy)
Legal page URL parameters work correctly (?tab=privacy, ?tab=terms)
Thank You page loads with appropriate content
Footer present on all pages with correct sections (Services, Resource, Company) and social media links
Hero section CTA buttons navigate correctly to forms
Home page CTA section buttons work correctly
Mobile hamburger menu opens and navigation works on small viewport (390x844)
All form validation works (required fields marked correctly)
No JavaScript errors or console warnings detected
